the submittal of an applicable implementation plan by a specific date. See CAA sections 169B(e)(2), 184 (b)(1) &amp;
(c)(5). However, EPA is proposing to treat Tribes in the same manner as States for all other interstate commission-related
provisions under sections 169B, 176A and 184 of the CAA. 
