<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
As discussed in Part II.B. above, EPA intends to provide Tribal air quality protection when Tribes do not develop such
programs. EPA's efforts will take place in a prioritized, phased-in fashion due to limitations on Federal resources.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

