<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) The number of participants acquiring the GED, high school diploma, and other certificates of performance. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) A narrative summary of the activities conducted under the project. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(4) Each Adult Education Office shall submit any records and information that the Director requires in connection
